<p>&quot;My name is Matthew Lin, and people also call me Matt, Matthew, or MattLin. I am a junior in CALS, majoring in biology, concentrating in general biology, and minoring in music, and education. In my free time I enjoy running around the various trails of the area, and tutoring down at Ithaca High School. Last year as the Arts RA, I mainly worked with The Shops and led the Arts Subcommittee. I learned a lot during my first year, but there&#39;s still plenty more to do! I hope to make all building spaces the best they can be, host several educational programs, and implement a few sustainability ideas. I&#39;m usually in common spaces, the RA Office, or in my room with the door open.</p>

